STL TECHNOLOGY C June Sales Fall 30.76% (Table) : 4931 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-07-08T07:40:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/stl-technology-c-june-sales-fall-30-76-table-4931-tt.html
STL TECHNOLOGY C said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 30.76% to NT$421,644,000 from NT$608,954,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            421,644          608,954    
YOY%             -30.76%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,872,644        3,811,056   
YOY%             -24.62% 
=================================================================
 